        <num>CC 2824</num>
        <heading>2824.  Payment of interest of partner</heading>
        <content>
          <p>Art. 2824.  Payment of interest of partner.
If a partnership continues to exist after the membership of a partner ceases, unless otherwise agreed, the partnership must pay in money the amount referred to in Article 2823 as soon as that amount is determined together with interest at the legal rate from the time membership ceases.</p>
        </content>
